criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:
1. Age:40-80，BMI<30kg/m2；
2. ASA grade:Ⅰ-Ⅲ；
3. Planning to receive laparoscopic gastrectomy；
4. General anesthesia and non-depolarizing muscle relaxant rocuronium bromide were given for endotracheal intubation and muscle relaxant maintenance.
5. Willing to sign informed consent.
Exclusion Criteria:
1. Preoperative history of diseases of digestive system such as inflammatory bowel disease and intestinal flora disorder;
2. Suffering severe heart, lung, liver, kidney or brain diseases;
3. serious infections , antibiotics should be used;
4. Have received abdominal surgery;
5. Combined with gravis myasthenia, serious electrolyte disorders or neuromuscular diseases.
